Life.quote: Each day is a new chance to rewrite your story. Make it amazing!
The morning is a magical time when all the possibilities of the day lie before you.
The morning is a gift. Don't waste it with worry or regret. Make the most of it and live every moment.
Your attitude is either the lock on, or the key to the door of success.
The only disability in life is a bad attitude.
